DOM Interview Questions for Automation Testers (4–5 Years Experience)


====================================================
SECTION 1: DOM Basics
====================================================
1. What is the DOM?
2. What does DOM stand for?
3. Is the DOM part of HTML or JavaScript?
4. How does a browser create the DOM?
5. What is the difference between HTML and DOM?


====================================================
SECTION 2: DOM Structure & Nodes
====================================================
6. What is the difference between element nodes, text nodes, and attribute nodes?
7. What is the root node of an HTML document?
8. What is the parent, child, and sibling relationship in the DOM?


====================================================
SECTION 3: DOM Selectors (Very Important for Automation)
====================================================
9. What are DOM selectors?
10. How do CSS selectors work with the DOM?
11. Give examples of commonly used CSS selectors in automation testing.


====================================================
SECTION 4: DOM & Automation Testing
====================================================
12. Why is DOM knowledge important for automation testers?
13. How do Playwright and Cypress interact with the DOM?
14. What happens in the DOM when a button is clicked?
15. How do you verify an element is present in the DOM?
16. What is the difference between an element existing in the DOM
    and being visible on the UI?
17. How do you handle dynamically changing DOM elements?
18. What is DOM re-rendering and how does it affect automation tests?
19. What causes stale element issues in automation testing?
20. How do you handle stale elements in Playwright or Cypress?


====================================================
SECTION 5: Shadow DOM (Advanced – Very Important)
====================================================
21. What is Shadow DOM?
22. Why is Shadow DOM used?
23. How do Playwright and Cypress handle Shadow DOM?
24. What challenges have you faced while automating Shadow DOM elements?


====================================================
SECTION 6: DOM Attributes & Properties
====================================================
25. What is the difference between attributes and properties in the DOM?
